com.hazelcast.spi

Interface ResponseHandler

  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface ResponseHandler
    A handler for the OperationService when it has calculated a response. This way you can hook into the system and decide what to do with it: for example, send it to the right machine. This interface is deprecated since Hazelcast 3.6. Use OperationResponseHandler instead.
